    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you hit a creature with a weapon attack, you can expend one superiority die to maneuver one of your comrades into a more advantageous position. You add the superiority die to the attack's damage roll, and you choose a friendly creature who can see or hear you. That creature can use its reaction to move up to half its speed without provoking opportunity attacks from the target of your attack.</p>\n<p><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:#191813;font-size:13px\">Note: After adding this feature to your character, edit this feature's details and set Resource Consumption to Items Uses: Combat Superiority.</em></p>\n<p>Â </p>",
